nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, on this hand clubs are trump so playing Kickback 4@D is RKCB (1 higher than the trump suit). The responses (assuming 0314) are 4@H = 0 or 3, 4@S = 1 or 4, 4N = 2 no Q, 5@C = 2 Key-cards with Q.|mb|4D|
