up|40|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|3@C is a reasonable bid by North since North's clubs are so much better than the diamonds. However, a 3@D overcall is possible because then it gives North room to bid 4@C. Generally when you have 2 suits of equal length you tend to bid the higher suit unless the lower one is strong and the higher one is weak. |
