cp|8|AT|^^
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I would still bid 4@S and feel better about it since we have a diamond fit. You should try for 4 of a major rather than 5 of a minor whenever possible. Granted, if North bid diamonds, 5@D is a better contract than 4@S.|
