nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|To answer another question, 3@S by me is forcing. But 4@S is pretty likely to be where I want to play. Granted we might have 6. However, once there is a preempt a good bidding principle is to worry about finding your best game and don't worry too much about bidding slam. |
